<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The law applicable to contracts relating to the activities referred to in the First Directive shall be the law of the Member State of the commitment. </inglise>
<eesti> Esimeses direktiivis nimetatud tegevuste suhtes kohaldatakse kohustuse liikmesriigi &otilde;igust. </eesti>
<inglise> However, where the law of that State so allows, the parties may choose the law of another country. </inglise>
