<inglise> In the event of an assurance undertaking being wound up, commitments arising from contracts underwritten by way of freedom to provide services shall be met in the same way as those arising from that undertaking's other assurance contracts, no distinction being made on grounds of the nationality of assured persons or beneficiaries. </inglise>
