<eesti> Artikkel 22 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Where an operation is offered by way of freedom to provide services, the policy-holder shall, before any commitment is entered into, be informed of the Member State in which the head office, agency or branch with which the contract is to be concluded is established. </inglise>
