<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Where the provision of services is conditional upon authorization by the Member State of provision of services, the amount of the technical reserves, including mathematical reserves, and the rules on profit sharing and on the surrender and paid-up values of the contracts concerned shall be determined under the supervision of that Member State in accordance with the rules it has laid down or, failing such rules, in accordance with established practice in that Member State. </inglise>
